671
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:02,749
Il va bien?

672
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:04,594
Malheureusement.

673
00:40:05,520 --> 00:40:06,919
Je devrais culpabiliser.

674
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,355
Surtout pas.

675
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:11,596
Pardon.

676
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:17,551
Matthew te réclame.
Il veut te dire bonjour.

677
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,949
Passe-le-moi.

678
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,788
Dis bonjour à papa.

679
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:23,714
Dis bonjour à papa...

680
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:25,395
<i>au téléphone.</i>

681
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:27,035
Parle dans le combiné.

682
00:40:30,120 --> 00:40:30,916
Dis bonjour.

683
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,229
Matthew?

684
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:33,756
Salut, bonhomme.

685
00:40:34,000 --> 00:40:36,389
